items.name: Bag Pipes
items.description: Your mom won't be able to wait to hear you practice!

items.name: Bangin' Headphones
items.description: Walk around town with the coolest headphones on the market. The only problem is that you won't be able hear people talk about how cool your headphones are.

items.name: Barbed Wire Fence
items.description: Trap your kids inside your yard with this barbed wire fence! They will never be able to escape and hurt themselves out in the real world. Instead they will just have to live with all of the emotional damage having you as a parent caused.

items.name: Bike Pump
items.description: Are your tires flat and sad? Give them some air with this state of the art bike pump! All of your friends will be jealous of how pumped up your tires are.

items.name: Dog
items.description: It goes 'roof' and sometimes 'woof'.

items.name: Hot Dog
items.description: It may need a quick trip in the microwave before you eat it. USDA approved.

items.name: Men's Dress Shoes
items.description: Dazzle everyone in the room with these premium leather dress shoes. Everyone will be like "OMG where did you get those shoes?"

items.name: Propeller Hat
items.description: It's a bird! No, it's a plane! Actally it's just some creepy guy wearing a propeller hat. Seriously, who invented these things?

items.name: VHS Player
